2. ISSUES RELATED TO SENTENCE
   	TRANSLATION ISSUE: It can be observed when the words are not properly aligned in various layers.
	OBSERVATION:-
 		a) Sentence Number: 2.39 FROM Geo_chap2_E1.
		   Translation Issue:'..from the view point of geology' should be translated to 'भूविज्ञान के दृष्टिकोण से'. However, it is being translated to 'भूगर्भ वैज्ञानिकों के अनुसार'

        b) Sentence number: 2.99 Geo_chap2_E1
		   Translation Issue:'..originate in the Himalaya' is translated to 'हिमालय से निकलती  है' It should be translated to 'हिमालय से उत्पन्नहोेती है'
 
 	PARAPHRASING: Paraphrases are sentences or phrases that convey the same meaning using different wordings.
 		    Paraphrasing is of TWO types:
    		1. UNNECCESARY PARAPHRASING: Unnecessary Paraphrasing arises during translation of sentences(say from ENG-HINDI) due to which sentence is unable to deliver a specific.
	          a) Sentence Number: 2.39 FROM Geo_chap2_E
     		  UNNECCESARY Paraphrasing- दृष्टिकोण मतलब से .However,it should be दृष्टिकोण से
    
   		   	2. NECCESARY PARAPHRASING: Necessary paraphrasing occurs when it becomes important to add some extra words while translation.The actual translated word could not hold or deliver a specfic meaning without forming a compound with other added word.
   
  	E CONSTRUCTION: Construction of english sentence changes during language translation.  
		a) Sentence Number: 2.64 Geo_chap2_E1.
		   	English sentence:"This range consists of the famous valley of Kashmir, the Kangra and Kullu Valley in Himachal Pradesh."
        	Hindi sentence: इसी शृङ्खला में कश्मीर की घाटी तथा हिमाचल के काङ्गडा एवं कुल्लू की घाटियाँ स्थित हैं .
		   	Construction: ','(comma) is doing task for 'तथा' in hindi

    H CONSTRUCTION: Construction of hindi sentence changes during language translation.
		a) Sentence Number: 2.64 Geo_chap2_E1.
		   	English sentence:"This range consists of the famous valley of Kashmir, the Kangra and Kullu Valley in Himachal Pradesh."
        	Hindi sentence: इसी शृङ्खला में कश्मीर की घाटी तथा हिमाचल के काङ्गडा एवं कुल्लू की घाटियाँ स्थित हैं .
		   	Construction: 'तथा' in hindi does not have any word equivalent in english.
  		 
   
  	ANUSAARAKA ISSUE: It is observed from the Kth layer. These issues involve the mis-construct of the tool while placing the translated words in the Kth layer.
		a) Sentence Number: 2.39 Geo_chap2_E1.
		   Anusaaraka Issue: 'From the view point of geology' is translated to दृष्टिकोण मतलब से, 'form' is aligned with बनाते  हुए

  	SENTENCE ALIGNMENT OBSERVATION: Alignment of the sentence in each layer is observed.
		a) Sentence Number: 2.39 Geo_chap2_E1.
		   Sentence alignment: Wrong alignment('From the view point of geology' is not properly aligned in Pth layer)

  	Pth OBSERVATION:Observe the Pth layer.
		a) Sentence Number: 2.39 Geo_chap2_E1.
