4.Solution by use/modification/addition of dictionary: 
		Some of the words are not present in dictionary or are present but having incorrect meaning or that word is having multiple meanings then in that case dictonary is updated or rules are written to replace or WSD rules are written in clips. For the dictionary issues we modify, add the words in dictonary.
    